{"tid":1612020,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"你哋連登仔有幾勇武，絕對毫無意義，國家繼續繁榮安定。所有負面消息已被國家防火牆刪除或屏蔽。","createTime":"2019-10-02T06:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:50:46.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b752fc78834daff6a903eac38b6ad9953dbb8635","tid":1612020,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"「因果由國」<br />\n你幾勇武，根本無意義<br />\n因為國家防火牆輕易將你的信息屏蔽過濾了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算死幾多人，大陸高官係冷氣房中甚麼都看不見，聽不到。<br />\n<br />\n中國人的網絡世界，天下太平，香港人在唱國歌慶祝新中國成立七十周年，祖國偉大，歌頌祖國，歌頌中共，祖國越來越強盛。<br />\n<br />\n你地班勇武又好，和理非又好，對準了香港政權，但沒有對準國家防火牆城，所以做咩都無用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人認為，香港人權民主法案唔夠。香港需要呼籲西方國家，推出《世界網絡自由及人權法》。<br />\n<br />\n唔信我，唔緊要<br />\n大家可以上上百度<br />\n搜尋香港就理解了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.baidu.com/sf/vsearch?pd=realtime&amp;word=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&amp;tn=vsearch&amp;sa=vs_tab&amp;lid=9363898527253336865&amp;ms=1&amp;from=844b&amp;atn=index&amp;ssid=0&amp;from=844b&amp;uid=0&amp;pu=usm@10,sz@320_1001,ta@iphone_2_9.0_24_77.0&amp;bd_page_type=1&amp;baiduid=00BEB0EB492147B819D91713BD0D022D&amp;tj=__0_10_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.baidu.com%2Fsf%2Fvsearch%3Fpd%3Drealtime%26word%3D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%26tn%3Dvsearch%26sa%3Dvs_tab%26lid%3D9363898527253336865%26ms%3D1%26from%3D844b%26atn%3Dindex%26ssid%3D0%26from%3D844b%26uid%3D0%26pu%3Dusm%4010%2Csz%40320_1001%2Cta%40iphone_2_9.0_24_77.0%26bd_page_type%3D1%26baiduid%3D00BEB0EB492147B819D91713BD0D022D%26tj%3D__0_10_4&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=033498b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.baidu.com/sf/vsearch?pd=realtime&amp;word=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&amp;tn=vsearch&amp;sa=vs_tab&amp;lid=9363898527253336865&amp;ms=1&amp;from=844b&amp;atn=index&amp;ssid=0&amp;from=844b&amp;uid=0&amp;pu=usm@10,sz@320_1001,ta@iphone_2_9.0_24_77.0&amp;bd_page_type=1&amp;baiduid=00BEB0EB492147B819D91713BD0D022D&amp;tj=__0_10_4</a>"},{"pid":"1abca17ed65a0da5ed7aae676c5bc6